# Master EJS, Dynamic Routing & Project Setup

- initialize a project with npm
  ```javascript
  npm init -y
  ```
- express install
  ```javascript
  npm i express
  ```

## Dynamic routing

- setting up parsers for form

  ```javascript
  app.use(express.json());
  app.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: true }));
  ```

- setting up ejs for fjs pages

  - install ejs from npm

  ```javascript
  npm i ejs
  ```

  - setup ejs as a middlware for view engine

  ```javascript
  app.set("view engine", "ejs");
  ```

- etting up public static files

  ```javascript
  app.use(express.static(Path2D.join(__dirname, "public")));
  ```

- dynamic routing
- how to get data coming from frontend at backend route
